Package cz.cuni.mff.desitka.dictionaries

package cz.cuni.mff.desitka.dictionaries
This package contains classes related to dictionaries and their interactions with Wiktionary. It includes the Dictionary class which extends the Wiktionary class and provides methods to interact with a dictionary. It also includes the Wiktionary class which provides methods to interact with Wiktionary.
